            <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
            <div class="faq-section">
                <h2>General Questions</h2>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What is Go-Eco?</h3>
                    <p>Go-Eco is a platform that encourages eco-friendly actions by rewarding users with points for completing green tasks. These points can be redeemed for eco-friendly rewards and users can compete on our leaderboard.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How does Go-Eco work?</h3>
                    <p>Users sign up, complete eco-friendly tasks, earn points, and redeem them for rewards. Tasks range from recycling initiatives to energy conservation activities and community service.</p>
                </div>

                <h2>Getting Started</h2>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I sign up?</h3>
                    <p>Click on the "Signup" link in the navigation bar, fill in the required details, and start your eco-friendly journey with Go-Eco.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Is there a fee to join?</h3>
                    <p>No, joining Go-Eco is completely free. Our goal is to make eco-friendly living accessible to everyone.</p>
                </div>

                <h2>Tasks and Points</h2>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What types of tasks can I complete?</h3>
                    <p>We offer a variety of tasks including recycling, energy-saving, water conservation, and community service activities. Check out our <a href="/tasks">Tasks</a> page for more details.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I earn points?</h3>
                    <p>Complete tasks listed on our platform and upload proof of completion (such as photos). Points will be awarded based on the taskâ€™s complexity and impact.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>Where can I see my points?</h3>
                    <p>Your total points and task history can be viewed in your profile section. Additionally, you can track your progress on the <a href="/leaderboard">leaderboard</a>.</p>
                </div>

                <h2>Rewards</h2>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What rewards can I earn?</h3>
                    <p>Rewards range from eco-friendly products to vouchers for sustainable brands. Visit our rewards page for the current list of available rewards.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do I redeem my points?</h3>
                    <p>Go to the rewards page, select the reward you want, and click on the redeem button. The required points will be deducted from your total.</p>
                </div>

                <h2>Support</h2>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What if I have trouble with a task?</h3>
                    <p>If you encounter any issues with a task or need further guidance, feel free to contact our support team through the contact form on our website.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How can I contact support?</h3>
                    <p>You can reach out to our support team via the contact form on our website or email us directly at support@go-eco.com.</p>
                </div>
